
!samples/messy/.gitkeep
.deps/
.playwright-mcp/
.tmp/
*.db
*.db.wal
*.log
**/.DS_Store
# ── database ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ── fetched public court documents (scripts/fetch-public.sh) ─────────────
# ── generated corpus (samples/gen/corpus.sql, run by scripts/setup.sh) ────
# ── local scratch (never vendor binaries) ────────────────────────────────
# ── OS / private ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ── page rasters (scripts/setup.sh via pdf_to_png) ───────────────────────
# ── redaction outputs + PDF lifecycle runtime (dir tree kept via .gitkeep) ─
# ── stress fixtures (tests/stress/01c_generate_folder.sql, 05_failure_modes.sql) ─
# ── test + tooling artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# closure.db holds the decision log (real reviewer state) alongside the corpus
# Everything below is an output. The inputs are server/**, static/**, samples/gen/**,
# One rule: if `make setup` can build it or fetch it, it is not tracked.
# Only stray rendered HTML is ignored; static/*.js is hand-authored and tracked.
# tables rebuilt from samples/ on every boot.
# tests/**, design/**, docs/**.
Alok_FDE*
data/**/_store_meta.json
data/export/*_redacted.pdf
data/source/*.pdf
data/working/*.pdf
data/working/registry/*.json
exports/*.pdf
exports/audit_sidecar.jsonl
exports/audit.db
exports/decisions/
exports/export_map.csv
node_modules/
nohup.out
pages/**/*.png
samples/*.pdf
samples/identities.json
samples/manifest.json
samples/messy/**
samples/public/_renders/
samples/public/*.pdf
samples/stress/*.err
samples/stress/*.pdf
samples/stress/fail/
samples/stress/glob/
samples/stress/glob20/
samples/stress/glob5/
samples/watchlist.json
static/*.html
test-results/
tests/e2e/playwright-report/
tests/e2e/test-results/

# DuckDB runtime
closure.db
closure.db.wal
closure.db.tmp/
